001package doctorwhoapp.backend.data.entities;
002
003import doctorwhoapp.backend.domain.Gender;
004import jakarta.persistence.Column;
005import jakarta.persistence.EnumType;
006import jakarta.persistence.Enumerated;
007import jakarta.persistence.MappedSuperclass;
008
009@MappedSuperclass
010public class PersonEntity extends BaseEntity {
011    @Column(nullable = false)
012    @Enumerated(EnumType.STRING)
013    private Gender gender;
014
015    public Gender getGender() {
016        return gender;
017    }
018
019    public void setGender(final Gender gender) {
020        this.gender = gender;
021    }
022}
